data.description: ** Ask us about the sellers' AMAZING VA ASSUMABLE RATE AT 2.75%!!! **  Nestled on over 3.6 acres of private wooded flat land, 4104 Green Spring St is a true sanctuary offering over 2,500 square feet of fully updated luxury living. From the moment you arrive, the natural setting and peaceful surroundings set the stage for the remarkable residence that awaits.  Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a sense of sophistication and modernity. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring crisp white cabinets, gleaming granite counters, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or preparing a quiet meal for yourself, this kitchen is both stylish and functional.  The allure of nature continues seamlessly with the addition of a captivating sunroom. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or enjoying a good book surrounded by the beauty of the outdoors, all from the comfort of your own home. This space offers a perfect blend of tranquility and comfort, creating an ideal retreat within your own four walls.  The fully finished lower level adds an extra dimension to this already impressive home. A full bedroom and bathroom provide privacy and convenience for guests or family members, while the bonus living space offers endless possibilities for recreation, a home office, or a media room. The 2-car garage ensures that you have ample space for your vehicles and additional storage needs.  Take a minute for yourself in your new deluxe primary suite. Generously proportioned, it provides a haven of relaxation with plenty of room to unwind. The spa-like ensuite attached to the primary suite adds a touch of luxury to your daily routine, creating a private oasis within your own home.  Beyond the walls of this exquisite property lies a sprawling backyard, a canvas for your outdoor dreams. Whether you envision lush gardens, a play area for children, or simply a serene escape, the possibilities are endless on this expansive piece of land.  Experience the seamless integration of luxury and nature, where modern amenities meet the tranquility of wooded surroundings. Your dream home awaits – schedule a showing today and embark on the next chapter of elegant living.  NEWER HVAC (2021), SEPTIC (2020), Water Heater (2021), Water Filter/Softener System (2021), Chimney Interior (2020), Kitchen, Bathrooms, Flooring, and more!
